{"tid":1481442,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：各位要珍惜這些美國支援，不要魯莽衝擊，遇事即刻走人，以免糟蹋了大好的國際社會支援。","createTime":"2019-08-17T17:08:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T15:50:29.000Z","uid":27036,"like":166,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"c148c0cedbe4518a399959cbb55f81da381f5319","tid":1481442,"uid":27036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:08:19.000Z","msg":"陳雲：明日維園集會前夕，美國前眾議院議長金里奇發言，呼籲全力支持香港人爭取自由。各位要珍惜這些美國支援，不要魯莽衝擊，遇事即刻走人，以免糟蹋了大好的國際社會支援。"},{"pid":"261c94b8f7df9b49f15d81d2bd1509c099e586b3","tid":1481442,"uid":41093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:09:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e24669d15818bff7d0438da0771f533a2550141","tid":1481442,"uid":72511,"like":24,"dislike":3,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:09:38.000Z","msg":"佢呢幾日食啱藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4351fad7f77c0b075a371c7def0e796736493aa9","tid":1481442,"uid":41093,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:09:54.000Z","msg":"係勇武換返黎嘅成果<br />\n跟番個勝利cycle 到和理非回合"},{"pid":"77b80d50cf40781a0a14a1032c4b774913d68c85","tid":1481442,"uid":168359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:27:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f2e7f2343206dcdb7ee2dd57adb11e0cf9ddd4","tid":1481442,"uid":7971,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:36:02.000Z","msg":"推，甜蛋糕係依幾日就知有無得食<br />\n無得食之後先再決定點行<br />\n聽日真係唔好衝"},{"pid":"14e23a57782537aca77bad4e114bd56c4014f68b","tid":1481442,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:38:02.000Z","msg":"有食藥"},{"pid":"5621f3fc8271e5d2c691bd032